channel.title: Tex2talk - Ambivalence
channel.description:
Hey everyone! This is just something I've been working on and off the past few months. to be completely honest I'm not really good at making the song flow, I've seen tracks made with auxy that I simply could not replicate.
Anyways, hopefully you'll enjoy this. Any criticism is appreciated. o/ https://soundcloud.com/tex2talk/ambivalence
